'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 68''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 68''',  is the sixty-eighth issue of ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', released on [[February 15]], [[2007]]. It contains 100 pages. It is the final issue of the magazine, as it was merged with ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' as part of [[Titan Magazines]]' acquisition of ''Insider''.

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Com-Scan]]
*[[Best of StarWars.com]]
*[[Jawa's Corner]]
*[[Star Wars Q&A|Q&A]]
*[[Refresher Reading]] &mdash; 20 Things You Didn't Know About The [[Chalmun's Spaceport Cantina/Legends|Mos Eisley Cantina]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 91}}
*[[Set Piece]] &mdash; X-Wing Starfighter {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 91}}

